    "Second, to study the ecological distribution of all plasmids and plasmid systems at the same time, we recruited each metagenome's reads to a fasta file that contained either the non-redundant set of 68,350 predicted plasmids or the non-redundant set of 11,121 reference plasmids.",
    "For computational efficiency, every read was aligned at most once (that is, the default behaviour of Bowtie).",
    "A plasmid was considered present in a metagenome if its detection was ≥0.95.",
